dc_title_s: The Balkans 1:250,000. Kerkira, sheet G-4. A.M.S. M506 (G.S.G.S. 4410)
dc_description_s: AMS 2. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4410. Alternate title: Kerkira.Transverse mercator projection. Universal transverse Mercator and Mediterranean zone grids. Principal meridians are Athens and Greenwich. UTM grid added, gradient tints and air information deleted by AMS, 1948. Relief shown by 100 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. With Albanian and Greek glossaries. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1948.
